⚔️ Difference Between sh and bash
Feature	sh (Bourne Shell)	bash (Bourne Again Shell)
Type	Older shell	Advanced shell
Features	Limited	Rich features
Arrays	❌ Not supported	✅ Supported
Syntax	Simple	More powerful
Usage	Basic scripting	Advanced scripting
Compatibility	Highly portable	Less portable than sh
